description: Sajj Street Eats fills you with the sights and aromas of sajj, pita, falafel and shawarma being made in front of you. It’s provides exotic Middle Eastern entrée choices you can customize any way you want. The menu includes authentic sauces and flavors you won’t find anywhere else. Sajj Street Eats shows you graciousness and warmth characteristic of Middle Eastern hospitality. And it’s healthy and fast, on the streets of San Francisco now.
name: Sajj Street Eats
